Short install instructions for RegCM v4

 -- copy the appropriate Makefile.inc.$ to Makefile.inc 
 -- edit the options if needed
 -- define a domain.param and put it in the RegCM base directory
 -- then type
    -- make terrain
    -- ./PreProc/Terrain/terrain
    -- make icbc
    -- make regcm
    -- make postproc

 -- you will be ready to run SST/ICBC for initial and boundary conditions 
    and then run RegCM

 -- make clean will clean all
